  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee in a pan and add the mincemeat, stirring to coat.",
    "Stir in cardamom and saffron; cook for about 5 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Rinse the rice and place it in a medium saucepan with water. Bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer until all the water is absorbed (about 10-12 minutes).",
    "Fold the cooked rice into the mincemeat mixture and stir well.",
    "If desired, serve warm over fresh fruit compote for an extra indulgent touch."
